<item>
            <title>[LU-929] add configure --with-ldiskfsprogs to e2fsprogs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-929</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This is an adaptation of the patches for bug:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22983&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://bugzilla.lustre.org/show_bug.cgi?id=22983&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Enables a new configure option (--with-ldiskfsprogs) which combined with the same option in lustre, allows e2fsprogs essential commands to be installed without conflicting e2fsprogs package on distribution&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12685">LU-929</key>
            <summary>add configure --with-ldiskfsprogs to e2fsprogs</summary>
